item.title: Solving Leviathan
item.description: After having done Bandit, let’s move on to Leviathan. None of the levels have hints, so there won’t be any links to each of the levels. Without further ado, let’s get cracking. Level 0 -> 1 Logging in with leviathan0:leviathan0 we take a quick look around to see what we have to work with, if anything leviathan0@melinda:~$ ls -la total 24 drwxr-xr-x 3 root root 4096 Nov 14 10:32 . drwxr-xr-x 167 root root 4096 Mar 21 06:46 ..
